{"tid":2083681,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇睇開ANISONG/J-pop DJ既巴打","createTime":"2020-06-29T02:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T12:39:06.000Z","uid":182353,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ccd0c857d94351d81a94f3aa96747c43e9ef5e39","tid":2083681,"uid":182353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:18:37.000Z","msg":"由之前Im@s cg 場live 請左DJ koo<br />\n開始接觸anisong DJ <br />\n再係武士道D4DJ到開始接觸多左<br />\n最近越睇越多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日笨大既asobinotes online fes<br />\n電音部 又公布左好多vtuber/聲優參加<br />\n相信黎緊應該會多好多人接觸anisong dj<br />\n所以開個po黎睇下有冇人討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647e0325f98bf97b51e13860099ff73ef1d4a6b3","tid":2083681,"uid":114487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HE0Php.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HE0Php.jpg&h=c5e5f272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"654c1bc3e8d68f2ef39e77ec3e27ad6e58668cd9","tid":2083681,"uid":182353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉先<br />\n我暫時有追既DJ就<br />\n<br />\n高木美佑<br />\n配過Wake Up, Girls!同D4DJ<br />\n最近係D4DJ同OMOTENASHI BEATS都有出過live <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8e-dOmq6JVo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8e-dOmq6JVo&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8X8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=877f5350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8e-dOmq6JVo</a><br />\n舊片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小宮有紗<br />\n成日拍特攝同埋配過LL水團<br />\n黎緊電音部都有份<br />\n最近係OMOTENASHI BEATS同琴日asobinotes都有出live<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U0Z1CO4Uq5E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU0Z1CO4Uq5E&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8X8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=4e77bacc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U0Z1CO4Uq5E</a><br />\n有興趣可以買黎聽下 <del>Apple music有</del><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋黎緊星期日 <br />\nOMOTENASHI BEATS都會係twitch直播<br />\nDJ koo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xN1VDGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxN1VDGe.jpg&h=61cd8e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/omotenashib/status/1276488041104695297?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fomotenashib%2Fstatus%2F1276488041104695297%3Fs%3D21&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8X8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=4e13dbe9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fomotenashib%2Fstatus%2F1276488041104695297%3Fs%3D21&h=b3706cdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/omotenashib/status/1276488041104695297?s=21</a><br />\n另外就係twitch既MOGRA<br />\n間唔中都會有唔同anisong DJ live睇"},{"pid":"086525bc344bfa9f5140482b151d3a71655a5148","tid":2083681,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"D4DJ燐舞曲幾正<br />\nlive幾帶動到氣氛<br />\n不過武士道旗下project<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d787fb14b2ed055f00fd7c91474666368023fffa","tid":2083681,"uid":182353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"086525bc344bfa9f5140482b151d3a71655a5148","tid":2083681,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"D4DJ燐舞曲幾正<br />\nlive幾帶動到氣氛<br />\n不過武士道旗下project<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:15:52.000Z","msg":"つんこ間唔中都有出dj live（唔係d4dj身份）<br />\n都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkg